# Day 17 Lab – Exploring SSH Fundamentals, Keys, Known Hosts & File Identification

## Date
20 July 2026

## Objective

Today's lab focuses on understanding the SSH environment already present on the system. No new SSH keys are generated and no configuration files are modified. The goal is to observe how SSH stores information and relate the practical observations with the theory learned today.

