# Experiment 1 – Exploring the SSH Directory

## Command

```bash
ls -la ~/.ssh
```

### Purpose

Display every file present inside the hidden SSH directory.

### Observation

Identify files such as:

- id_ed25519
- id_ed25519.pub
- known_hosts

Check whether an authorized_keys file exists.

